:Violets are blue.
:Onions stink.
:And so do you.<ref name=Hopscotch>"[http://www.hopscotch.com.au/hopscotch-articles/2005/5/18/jill-still-playing-jacks-and-hopscotch-endures/ Jill Still Playing Jacks And Hopscotch Endures] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hopscotch.com.au/hopscotch-articles/2005/5/18/jill-still-playing-jacks-and-hopscotch-endures/ |date=20090914170307 }}", retrieved 17 September 2009.</ref>
